debugger now also supports dictionary expressions
commits.body:
given this example:

```robot
*** Variables ***
&{DICTIONARY_EXAMPLE1}      output_dir=${OUTPUT DIR}
...                         AA=${DUT_IP_ADDRESS_1}
...                         ZZ=${{{1:2, 3:4}}}
```

now you can also evaluate expressions like

```
${DICTIONARY_EXAMPLE1}[output_dir]
```

in the debugger.
